    <item>
      <title>以色列和哈马斯将战争休战期再延长一天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/israel-and-hamas-extend-their-war-truce-for-another-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列和哈马斯同意将休战期至少再延长一天，以便释放加沙激进组织扣押的更多人质。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/israel-and-hamas-extend-their-war-truce-for-another-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 05:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界正在与以色列-哈马斯战争引发的仇恨犯罪浪潮作斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-11-30/antisemitism-islamophobia-rise-around-world-amid-israel-hamas-conflict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯的袭击和以色列在加沙的军事反应正在助长反犹太主义和仇视伊斯兰教，其速度超出了政府的反应速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-11-30/antisemitism-islamophobia-rise-around-world-amid-israel-hamas-conflict</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 05:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
