    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基在乌克兰进攻陷入停滞中面临人力困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/zelenskiy-faces-manpower-dilemma-in-ukraine-s-stalled-offensive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自六月以来，一项征召更多乌克兰男子参军的计划一直摆在总统泽连斯基的办公桌上。迄今为止，这位战时领导人顶住了军方的压力签署了该协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-30/zelenskiy-faces-manpower-dilemma-in-ukraine-s-stalled-offensive</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚债务成本给 2024 年预算中的社会支出带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/nigeria-debt-costs-pressures-social-spending-in-2024-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚明年用于偿还债务的支出将比这个西非国家修建新学校或医院的支出至少多六倍，该国40%以上的人口生活在极端贫困之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/nigeria-debt-costs-pressures-social-spending-in-2024-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 18:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
